/\">2D platform game using Phaser</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Publishing games</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Games/Publishing_games\">Publishing games overview</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Games/Publishing_games/Game_distribution\">Game distribution</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Games/Publishing_games/Game_promotion\">Game promotion</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Games/Publishing_games/Game_monetization\">Game monetization</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    \n    <li><a class=\"button minimal only-in-en-us\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Create_the_Canvas_and_draw_on_it\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">下一页  » (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>在这里我们将完全使用 JavaScript 语言基于 HTML5 的 canvas 标签，一步一步的绘制一个简单的 MDN 消除游戏。</p>\n<p>过程中的每一步都会有例子可供体验，让你更清晰的了解他的制作过程。你将学习到如何使用 canvas 标签的基本语法去实现简单游戏的渲染、动画、碰撞、控制胜负。</p>\n<p>为了更快速高效的学习本系列教程，你需要掌握 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/Getting_started_with_the_web/JavaScript_basics\">JavaScript</a> 的一些基础知识。学习完本教程之后你就可以创建自己的网页小游戏了。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/mdn-breakout-gameplay.png\" alt=\"Gameplay screen from the game MDN Breakout where you can use your paddle to bounce the ball and destroy the brick field, with keeping the score and lives.\" width=\"480\" height=\"320\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"教程详情","title":"教程详情","isH3":false,"content":"<p>全部教程 — <a href=\"http://breakout.enclavegames.com/lesson10.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MDN 消除小游戏</a> 的各个版本我们正一起管理并托管到 <a href=\"https://github.com/end3r/Canvas-gamedev-workshop\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">GitHub</a> 上：</p>\n<ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Create_the_Canvas_and_draw_on_it\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">创建、绘制画布 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Move_the_ball\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">让球动起来 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Bounce_off_the_walls\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">反弹的墙 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Paddle_and_keyboard_controls\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">键盘操作 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Game_over\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">游戏结束 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Build_the_brick_field\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">创建砖块 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Collision_detection\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">撞击处理 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Track_the_score_and_win\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">统计得分、获得胜利 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Mouse_controls\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">鼠标控制 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Finishing_up\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">完成 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>对于实现一个网页游戏而言，最好的方式是从纯 JavaScirpt 着手，那样可以让我们建立更坚实的基础。之后你可以在你的项目中选择你喜欢的框架。框架也只是用 JavaScript 语言实现的工具；如果你想要在项目中使用框架，你必须先了解语言本身。框架可以帮你提高开发效率并生成一些基础的内容；但是如果没有达到你的预期，你只能慢慢调试或者使用原生 JavaScript 去实现解决方案。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 如果你对使用第三方游戏资源库开发 2d 网页游戏感兴趣，可以参考本系列教程的 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_breakout_game_Phaser\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">2D breakout game using Phaser (en-US)</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 本系列教程可以用作游戏开发工作室的素材资源。如果你想探讨普通的游戏开发，你可以利用<a href=\"https://github.com/end3r/Gamedev-Canvas-Content-Kit\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamedev Canvas Content Kit</a>以及本教程的内容。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"下一步","title":"下一步","isH3":false,"content":"<p>好，让我们开始吧。第一步 — <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Create_the_Canvas_and_draw_on_it\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">创建、绘制画布 (en-US)</a></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    \n    <li><a class=\"button minimal only-in-en-us\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript/Create_the_Canvas_and_draw_on_it\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">下一页  » (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"教程详情","id":"教程详情"},{"text":"下一步","id":"下一步"}],"summary":"在这里我们将完全使用 JavaScript 语言基于 HTML5 的 canvas 标签，一步一步的绘制一个简单的 MDN 消除游戏。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"2D breakout game using pure JavaScript","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Famoso juego 2D usando JavaScript puro","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Jeu de casse-briques 2D en pur JavaScript","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"純粋な JavaScript を使ったブロック崩しゲーム","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"순수한 자바스크립트를 이용한 2D 벽돌깨기 게임","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"2D breakout game using 